room_title: Escape room "Speakeasy" by Escape Room Woodbridge in Arlington (VA)
room_description:
Looks like the big boss has just received word that a raid on other local Speakeasy's has got your location on the radar. Now you & your team have been hired to not only clean up the joint, but also find the hidden loot. Better hurry! The FBI Enforcer will be here in 60 minutes.

Can you take the money & run?
